@global.app_name is a free app version of the Parenting for Lifelong Health for Young Children programme and designed for parents and caregivers of children aged 2 to 9 years.

@global.app_name is brought to you by the collaboration of partners including Parenting for Lifelong Health, University of Oxford, IDEMS International, INNODEMS, and the Child Protection Office in the Ministry of Health - State of Kuwait (‘the @global.app_name team’).

Please read this @global.privacy_policy carefully. By downloading or using the app, you agree to the collection and use of information in relation to this policy. By using the @global.app_name, you agree to these terms. Please read the policy before sharing any information.

The terms used in this @global.privacy_policy have the same meanings as in our @global.terms_and_conditions, which are accessible within the app, unless otherwise defined in this @global.privacy_policy.

