SourceText:
The content in this app, such as text, images, and information, is for general educational purposes only. It is not a substitute for professional medical advice, diagnosis, treatment, or in-person visits to your doctor. @global.app_name is here to support, not replace, your relationship with your healthcare or other professional provider.

The information provided is not medical advice and should not be used for diagnosing or treating any health problems. Always consult your doctor regarding any medical concerns you have, and never ignore professional advice based on something you read here. If you think your child might have a medical emergency, contact a doctor or call 112 immediately.

@global.app_name is meant for healthy children without known medical conditions. If any health issues arise, follow up with your child’s healthcare provider, as the app may not be relevant. Using the app is at your own risk.

